Pop3Cli is an application which shows
how to use the TPop3Cli object to access
EMail on the Internet using the POP3
protocol (used by every ISP).
This one is compatible with all Delphi
version (1, 2, 3 and 4) and also 
C++Builder (1, 3, and 4).
The author can be contacted
at francois.piette@pophost.eunet.be. 
Support and updates can be found 
at http://www.rtfm.be/fpiette.
Unzip using the -d option to restore
directory tree. 
Freeware with full source code.

